name: LEOONO by Virtuals
description: Leoono is an AI-driven investment agent built to simplify and enhance stock analysis for everyone. It uses exclusive alternative data and insider trading insights that were previously only available to institutional investors. Leoono empowers retail investors with clear, actionable strategies, peer comparisons, and market insights. With over four years of experience supporting financial services across Europe and the Middle East, Leoono combines advanced technology with proven expertise to make smarter investing accessible to all.
